column5: Lake Huron Fishing Club Kincardine Hatchery updated Video, I needed to go up to get the New Cooler/Chiller last night for the Sacred Heart High School & Thought I'd get some Video, the Brown Trout Trays look really good & the Rainbow Tanks are before they are separated & Counted & one has the smaller ones after separated, there was still a bunch to be sorted by the weekend, before the Steelheaders Clip there fins Thanx & Tight Lines Richard     http://lhfcschoolhat...s.blogspot.com/
Sorry Richard but the link does not work for me... it prompts to "Sign in to YouTube"
Opps Problem fixed, Switched to LHFC Blog Sorry SBK
Super cool  The brown hatchery tray reminds me of when the little brown ants decide to all sunbathe and come out to the surface during the summer months.
Over 20,000 Browns in that one tray SBK
